  "remarks": "KPi.008. Tanchon Commercial Bank (TCB) official. Passport no: 645120196, issued in Democratic People's Republic of Korea. Ra Ky'ong-Su is a Tanchon Commercial Bank (TCB) official. In this capacity he has facilitated transactions for TCB. Tanchon was designated by the Committee in April 2009 as the main DPRK financial entity responsible for sales of conventional arms, ballistic missiles, and goods related to the assembly and manufacture of such weapons.; Listing: First listed on 22/01/2013 (amended on 02/03/2016, 26/07/2022 and 29/06/2023)",
